# Drop IBApi.dll here

The build expects `IBApi.dll` (and optionally `IBApi.pdb`) in this folder.
You can copy it from your TWS API install, typically:

  C:\TWS API\source\CSharpClient\IBApi\bin\Release\netstandard2.0\IBApi.dll

If the file is missing the build still succeeds — `FakeIbClient` is registered
by default and the app will run with synthesized bars.

Setting `InteractiveBrokers:UseRealClient = true` in `appsettings.json`
switches to the real client (the DLL must be present at that point).
